what_worked: Applied or_to_union, intersect_to_exists: Created filtered CTEs for highly selective dimensions (customer_address by city, income_band by bounds), then joined to customer and store_returns. Removed redundant customer_demographics bridge table by joining store_returns directly on c_current_cdemo_sk.
why_it_worked: Converting OR to UNION ALL lets optimizer choose independent index paths per branch; Replacing INTERSECT with EXISTS avoids materializing full intermediate sets
